testsuite.name: CourseRepository Sorting Tests

testcase.name: sortByStartDate should sort courses by start date
Sorting empty repository should return empty list
sortByCredits should sort courses by credits ascending
sortByDescription should sort courses by description using lambda
Sorting should not modify the original repository
sortByTitle should sort courses by title
sortByCreditsDesc should sort courses by credits descending
sortByCreditsAndDate should sort by credits desc, then by date
